title: Wedding Day Winners
overview: Each week in Wedding Day Winners, two happy couples poised to tie the knot, and their friends and family go head to head in order to win fabulous prizes, a dream honeymoon, and most importantly the most extraordinary wedding ceremony ever which will be broadcast to the nation.There are no losers in Wedding Day Winners. Each couple will come away with a host of prizes, happy memories and above all married to the love of their lives!
